 Shopify Point of Sale app extensions
 Shopify Point of Sale (POS) app extensions make it easy for developers to extend their app code into Shopify POS and customize many aspects of the POS experience. Shopify provides the tools and resources for building POS UI Extensions, cart app extensions, and product recommendation extensions.
 Explore the following references to learn more about building for Shopify POS.
